attributes.Long form description: The student starts assembling the two side legs and screws them with a screwdriver, then starts assembling the base frame with the help of the instructor. The student places the side legs into the base frame and used a screwdriver to screw the screws. He places the bottom grid tray between the side legs and uses bolts, brackets and hexagon cap nuts to assemble it. The student align the middle grid tray and later the top grid tray, then used bolts, brackets and hexagon cap nuts to assemble the trays to the side legs. He inspects the result, rotates the utility cart and started assembling the wheels to the base frame and when he finish assembled the utility cart and leave it on the table.
